Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to reach 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' before 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to transition to any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to be followed by 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where re-submission occurs

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' in successful claim processes

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to the next activity in the most frequent process variant

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in the shortest process variant

Name: Average time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' in processes ending with 'Payment Handled' without prior rejections

Name: Total time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' in processes with at least one rejection by any role
